p8?filename=9E0L2Z3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9E0L2Z3.jpg&h=b8df5dcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n淨返一餐咋...</blockquote><br />\n  <br />\n<br />\n乾糧 orijen <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.orijen.ca/foods/cat-food/dry-cat-food/cat-kitten/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.orijen.ca%2Ffoods%2Fcat-food%2Fdry-cat-food%2Fcat-kitten%2F&d=QPwT%2ByELcvOQ3V%2B17dE42XvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=c3300f77\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.orijen.ca/foods/cat-food/dry-cat-food/cat-kitten/</a><br />\n<br />\n加拿大貨<br />\n睇過咁多乾糧呢隻算最健康<br />\n冇乜致肥嘅碳水化合物<br />\n啲肉新鮮<br />\n冇乜filler<br />\n<br />\n不過可以嘅話至少餵一半濕糧<br />\n因為貓未必識渴<br />\n唔夠水腎同尿道好易出事<br />\n尤其係仔"},{"pid":"52172079ac0e9e36588e1d77f4953bc995efd0ef","tid":88342,"uid":3180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T16:33:18.000Z","msg":"主食乾糧：<br />\nOven baked traditional全貓糧<br />\nWellness core原味幼貓糧<br />\n<br />\n想靚毛就溝啲牛油果，食得多唔好所以隔日溝少少俾佢地<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYGKAhXwwuNjqTDwHXvaAWAqS4E19FEKJ9SR1vvGdeNQv?filename=8RA899L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8RA899L.jpg&h=f5ce357f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9c7c03f1978edc5fe81ed692bcab4aab55ba7c92","tid":88342,"uid":42564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T01:01:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>就黎4個月嘅布偶仔，啲糧就食哂，有冇介紹？<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdNYW8DagdsQPxhEzWC5SZhDUw8KHyBcPQEtExJNQ6BgR?filename=663833T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F663833T.jpg&h=153cff95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食開呢一隻，食到隻貓仔成日放臭屁...........<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/20/221703_8efd43ca9cebfbadbfbab453c65569ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F20%2F221703_8efd43ca9cebfbadbfbab453c65569ec.jpg&h=efd77c05&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"ht